@startuml Recruiter_Authentication

title Recruiter - Authentication (Module A)

actor Recruiter as "👔 Nhà Tuyển Dụng"

rectangle "AUTHENTICATION" {
    usecase "Register as\nRecruiter" as A2
    usecase "Login" as A3
    usecase "Logout" as A4
    usecase "Refresh Token" as A5
    usecase "Forgot\nPassword" as A6
    usecase "Reset Password" as A7
    usecase "Verify Email" as A8
}

Recruiter --> A2: 1. Register
Recruiter --> A3: 2. Login
A3 --> A5: Keep session
Recruiter --> A4: 3. Logout
Recruiter --> A6: Forgot password?
A6 --> A7: 4. Reset password
Recruiter --> A8: 5. Verify email

note right of A2
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Implemented ✅
end note

@enduml
